  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK670">
<l>eṉaittiṭpa meytiyak kaṇṇum viṉaittiṭpam </l>
<l>vēṇṭārai vēṇṭā tulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great will not esteem those who esteem not firmness of action, whatever other abilities the latter may possess.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
